As TUSCON lunged out, BIG CONVOY, MACH KICK and BREAK stepped out as
well, firing lasers up and around TUSCON targeting the SHARKTICON
guards.

Quickly the guards are dispatched!

The lead one is caught by TUSCON and sent flying back into two others
while the rest are caught by the laser fire from MACH KICK and BREAK.

BIG CONVOY backs up TUSCON as well, his own firepower, while tightly
controlled in this tight quarter, is powerful and forceful as he
opened up with his laser cannons.

Soon enough the SHARKTICONS are lying in heaps strewn about the floor
and the walls are scortched from the exchange of energy that came
through. There are also various dents and abrasions are on the wall
from where SHARKTICONS were caught and thrown into it.

The door they came through still stands open.

